hits.Instructions:
The goal of the game is to destroy all zombies and monsters.
Find new weapons in the boxes.
Upgrade characters and weapons to defeat strong enemies.

Q (K) - change weapons;
W, A, S, D (arrows) - move;
E (M) - apply / activate;
F (J) - super weapon.
LeftCntrl, Space (RightControl, KeyPad 0) - shooting;
Mouse - look / shoot;
For mobile devices, use touch input.

Q - change weapons;
A, D (left and right arrows) - move;
E - apply / activate;
W (space) - jump, press again double jump;
S (down arrow) - crouch.
Mouse - aim / shoot;
For mobile devices, use touch input.

Collect stars on the levels to unlock the coolest cars and participate in the leaderboard.

Use the pause menu to enter the garage or the map, as well as to control the sound in racing, derby, ramp jumping and free riding around the city.

PC Management:
W or forward arrow - gas;
A or left arrow - turn left;
S or back arrow - brake / reverse movement;
D or right arrow - turn right;

Management on mobile devices:
Using the control buttons on the screen

